#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Verambhasutta → verambā (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Verambhasutta"
msgstr "9. Gale-force Winds"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … adhigamāya."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

#. VAR: verambhā → verambā (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.9:1.3"
msgid "Upari, bhikkhave, ākāse verambhā nāma vātā vāyanti."
msgstr "High in the sky there are gale-force winds blowing."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.4"
msgid "Tattha yo pakkhī gacchati tamenaṃ verambhā vātā khipanti."
msgstr "Any bird that flies there is flung about by those gale-force winds."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.5"
msgid ""
"Tassa verambhavātakkhittassa aññeneva pādā gacchanti, aññena pakkhā "
"gacchanti, aññena sīsaṃ gacchati, aññena kāyo gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Their feet go one way, their wings another, their head another, and their "
"body another."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūto "
"pariyādiṇṇacitto pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya gāmaṃ vā "
"nigamaṃ vā piṇḍāya pavisati arakkhiteneva kāyena arakkhitāya vācāya "
"arakkhitena cittena, anupaṭṭhitāya satiyā, asaṃvutehi indriyehi."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, take a certain monk whose mind is overcome and overwhelmed "
"by possessions, honor, and popularity. He robes up in the morning and, "
"taking his bowl and robe, enters the village or town for alms without "
"guarding body, speech, and mind, without establishing mindfulness, and "
"without restraining the sense faculties."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.7"
msgid "So tattha passati mātugāmaṃ dunnivatthaṃ vā duppārutaṃ vā."
msgstr "There he sees a female scantily clad, with revealing clothes."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.8"
msgid ""
"Tassa mātugāmaṃ disvā dunnivatthaṃ vā duppārutaṃ vā rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti."
msgstr "Lust infects his mind."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.9"
msgid "So rāgānuddhaṃsitena cittena sikkhaṃ paccakkhāya hīnāyāvattati."
msgstr "He rejects the training and returns to a lesser life."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.10"
msgid ""
"Tassa aññe cīvaraṃ haranti, aññe pattaṃ haranti, aññe nisīdanaṃ haranti, "
"aññe sūcigharaṃ haranti, verambhavātakkhittasseva sakuṇassa."
msgstr ""
"Some take his robe, others his bowl, others his sitting cloth, others his "
"needle case, just like the bird flung about by the gale-force winds."

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.9:1.12"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.9:1.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
